title: 100: Stock Up, Stock Down
itunes:title: 100: Stock Up, Stock Down
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks share the latest draft movements for the biggest prospects in this year’s NFL draft in this week's  “Stock Up, Stock Down”. Plus, they break the tie for prospects with the same draft grade and give us key names to look out for in the 2017 NFL Draft.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
